data.description: Welcome to this cozy home in the welcoming town of Gaines! This 2-bed, 1-bath house sits on almost an acre of beautiful land, offering a peaceful escape from city life. With a comfy interior, spacious kitchen, and bedrooms designed for relaxation, it's the perfect mix of comfort and charm. Step outside to explore the big yard and enjoy the peaceful surroundings. Don't miss out ? come see this lovely home today and experience the inviting atmosphere of small town living at its best!
